! abbr="5-year" colspan="2" | Five-year survival (%)
|- style="background: #E5AFAA;text-align:center;font-size:90%;"
! abbr="NSCLC" | Non-small-cell lung carcinoma
! abbr="SCLC" | Small-cell lung carcinoma
